        "prompt": "Use case: illustration-story. Asset type: 16:9 Story Stones game backdrop. Primary request: Bluebell Acorn Village, a tiny woodland village of acorn-roof cottages, winding paths, mossy fences, and a broad empty village green; bluebells nodding beside the path. Style/medium: cosy children's picture-book illustration, hand-painted gouache and coloured-pencil texture on warm paper, chunky charcoal contours, charming imperfect brush marks, matching the approved Story Stones seed 1337 art direction. Composition/framing: wide 16:9 view with a broad uncluttered lower-centre performance clearing and environmental detail around the edges. Lighting/mood: soft blue morning light, gentle, magical, welcoming for ages 3–7. Constraints: environment only; preserve a clear floor for three separately composited story-stone sprites. Avoid: characters, creatures, people, food or loose hero objects in the performance area, text, letters, logo, watermark, UI, border, collage, photorealism, 3D.",
