      },
      "beats": [
        {
          "id": "beginning",
          "narrator": "story-dragon--friendly-monster--orange-cat-beginning",
          "text": "At Bluebell Acorn Village, Friendly Dragon discovered that the little bridge had lost a plank. So Friendly Dragon fanned its orange wings."
        },
        {
          "id": "complication",
          "narrator": "story-dragon--friendly-monster--orange-cat-complication",
          "text": "Then the stream began burbling faster, and Orange Cat hurried over. Orange Cat listened with forward whiskers; Friendly Dragon drew a glowing tail-curl; soon they had a clever crossing."
        },
        {
          "id": "resolution",
          "narrator": "story-dragon--friendly-monster--orange-cat-resolution",
          "text": "Friendly Monster finished the plan and gave one gentle lift. Soon, the bridge rested safely between both banks. Cottage windows glowed while the village played happy music."
        }
      ]
