        "prompt": "Use case: illustration-story. Asset type: 16:9 Story Stones game backdrop. Primary request: Velvet Cloudberry Bakery, an outdoor woodland bakery with berry-shaped ovens, floury bunting, a cobbled courtyard, and an uncluttered central floor; velvety moss covering the quiet banks. Style/medium: cosy children's picture-book illustration, hand-painted gouache and coloured-pencil texture on warm paper, chunky charcoal contours, charming imperfect brush marks, matching the approved Story Stones seed 1337 art direction. Composition/framing: wide 16:9 view with a broad uncluttered lower-centre performance clearing and environmental detail around the edges. Lighting/mood: soft plum twilight, gentle, magical, welcoming for ages 3–7. Constraints: environment only; preserve a clear floor for three separately composited story-stone sprites. Avoid: characters, creatures, people, food or loose hero objects in the performance area, text, letters, logo, watermark, UI, border, collage, photorealism, 3D.",
        "seed": 83980056,
        "workflow": "krea2-turbo-t2i",
        "width": 1344,
        "height": 768,
        "steps": 8,
        "cfg": 1
      },
      "beats": [
        {
          "id": "beginning",
          "narrator": "story-croissant--dragon--wishing-star-beginning",
          "text": "At Velvet Cloudberry Bakery, Friendly Dragon saw that the breakfast bell would not ring. With a hopeful smile, Friendly Dragon puffed a bright spark."
        },
        {
          "id": "complication",
          "narrator": "story-croissant--dragon--wishing-star-complication",
          "text": "Croissant noticed that a floury breeze crossed the courtyard. Side by side, Friendly Dragon warmed the air and Croissant sprinkled helpful crumbs, creating a neat loop."
        },
        {
          "id": "resolution",
          "narrator": "story-croissant--dragon--wishing-star-resolution",
          "text": "For the final touch, Wishing Star sparkled around the gap. At once, the bell rang three buttery notes. The ovens puffed sweet clouds and the bunting danced."
        }
      ]
    },
