          "narrator": "story-dragon--golden-key--rose-complication",
          "text": "The puzzle grew trickier when the harbour breeze changed direction. Friendly Dragon lifted one piece carefully, and Magic Rose bloomed at each kind idea, until they saw a path to shore."
