        "height": 768,
        "steps": 8,
        "cfg": 1
      },
      "beats": [
        {
          "id": "beginning",
          "narrator": "story-croissant--orange-cat--rose-beginning",
          "text": "At Velvet Lantern Library, Orange Cat saw that all the story lanterns had gone dim. With a hopeful smile, Orange Cat rolled a loose piece back."
        },
        {
          "id": "complication",
          "narrator": "story-croissant--orange-cat--rose-complication",
          "text": "Croissant joined just as the shelves hid the tallest lantern. Orange Cat followed tiny paw-marks, and Croissant sprinkled helpful crumbs, making a trail of light."
        },
        {
          "id": "resolution",
          "narrator": "story-croissant--orange-cat--rose-resolution",
          "text": "Magic Rose finished the plan and filled the air with courage. Soon, every lantern shone above its shelf. Books fluttered their pages around the reading circle."
        }
      ]
    },
