        "width": 1344,
        "height": 768,
        "steps": 8,
        "cfg": 1
      },
      "beats": [
        {
          "id": "beginning",
          "narrator": "story-friendly-monster--magic-bag--owl-beginning",
          "text": "At Bluebell Silver Reed Marsh, Friendly Monster discovered that the stepping islands had floated apart. So Friendly Monster stretched both long arms."
        },
        {
          "id": "complication",
          "narrator": "story-friendly-monster--magic-bag--owl-complication",
          "text": "Then the reeds hid the farthest island, and Meadow Owl hurried over. Meadow Owl called a clear hoot; Friendly Monster hummed a friendly note; soon they had a safe water route."
        },
        {
          "id": "resolution",
          "narrator": "story-friendly-monster--magic-bag--owl-resolution",
          "text": "One thing remained: Magic Bag produced a soft ribbon. That helped, and the islands formed a winding path. Frogs hummed while the marsh signs spun with delight."
        }
      ]
