      "beats": [
        {
          "id": "beginning",
          "narrator": "story-friendly-monster--golden-key--rose-beginning",
          "text": "At Peppermint Silver Reed Marsh, Friendly Monster discovered that the stepping islands had floated apart. So Friendly Monster stretched both long arms."
        },
        {
          "id": "complication",
          "narrator": "story-friendly-monster--golden-key--rose-complication",
          "text": "Magic Rose brought a new idea, but the reeds hid the farthest island. Friendly Monster hummed a friendly note, while Magic Rose filled the air with courage, making a safe water route."
        },
        {
          "id": "resolution",
          "narrator": "story-friendly-monster--golden-key--rose-resolution",
          "text": "Golden Key took a turn and spun toward the answer. Together, all three made sure the islands formed a winding path. Frogs hummed while the marsh signs spun with delight."
